Careful! 

These are not just marks - these are cracks! You will have a lot of future problems if that is not rectified correctly. 

The technician is trying to cheat by giving the false information that paint will hide it. The cracks are in the plaster and will always come back. You see that they were trying to hide it already. That is very negligent. 

Check our group guide about cracks in walls.
